1111 This bill amends the Freedom of Access Act by requiring a request submitted by 3 or
1122 more Legislators to be complied with within 20 working days as long as at least 3 of the
1133 Legislators are members of the Legislature's government oversight committee and one of
1144 those 3 members is one of the chairs of that committee. Current law requires the agency
